title: Investigation of Recipe Ratings and Features
description: Cooking is an essential part of daily life, yet consistently preparing delicious dishes can be challenging. According to a survey by the New York Post, the average American spends over 37 minutes daily cooking, highlighting significant effort and investment in meal preparation. Given this, I aim to uncover which recipe attributes most strongly influence user ratings by analyzing two large datasets of recipes and ratings from Food.com.
